README
------

* bars-horizontal.py				how to display bars as a graph
* plot-simple-graph.py				plot a simple graph
* plot-simple-graph-red.py			... red colour
* plot-simple-graph-red-stars.py		... red colour, data points as stars
* plot-simple-graph-red-decoration.py		... red colour, decorate plot, default values
* plot-simple-graph-red-decoration-mix.py	... red colour, decorate plot, customized
* plot-simple-graph-blue-o.py			... blue colour, data points as circles
* plot-simple-graph-green-dotted.py		... green colour, dotted line
* plot-simple-graph-as-subplot.py		plot two graphs as separate graphs
